@startuml
title CRM - UML Deployment Diagram

skinparam shadowing false
skinparam linetype ortho
skinparam nodesep 45
skinparam ranksep 55
skinparam padding 6
skinparam pageMargin 10
skinparam artifact {
  Padding 8
  Margin 8
}
skinparam node {
  Padding 10
  Margin 10
}
left to right direction
scale max 2480*1748

actor "CRM user" as User

node "Client device" as ClientDevice <<device>> {
  artifact "Browser or API client" as Browser <<artifact>>
}

node "Application host" as AppHost <<device>> {
  node "Docker container / ASP.NET Core process" as CrmRuntime <<executionEnvironment>> {
    artifact "Crm.dll" as CrmDll <<artifact>>
    artifact "appsettings.json" as Settings <<artifact>>
    artifact "ml-models directory" as Models <<artifact>>
  }
}

node "PostgreSQL host" as PgHost <<device>> {
  node "PostgreSQL runtime" as PgRuntime <<executionEnvironment>> {
    database "crm_db" as CrmDb
  }
}

node "Identity provider host" as IdpHost <<device>> {
  node "Keycloak runtime" as KeycloakRuntime <<executionEnvironment>>
}

node "Observability host" as ObsHost <<device>> {
  together {
    node "OTLP Collector" as Collector <<executionEnvironment>>
    node "Jaeger" as Jaeger <<executionEnvironment>>
  }
  together {
    node "Prometheus" as Prometheus <<executionEnvironment>>
    node "Grafana" as Grafana <<executionEnvironment>>
  }
  node "stdout / log collector" as Logs <<executionEnvironment>>
}

node "Import data location" as ImportHost <<device>> {
  artifact "Shopping trends source file" as Csv <<artifact>>
}

User --> Browser : работает с CRM
Browser --> CrmRuntime : HTTPS REST\n8080/8081

CrmRuntime --> PgRuntime : TCP 5432\nEF Core / Npgsql
PgRuntime --> CrmDb : хранит данные

CrmRuntime --> KeycloakRuntime : HTTP 8080\nJWT/OIDC и Admin API
CrmRuntime --> Collector : OTLP traces\n4317
Collector --> Jaeger : передает трассировки
Prometheus --> CrmRuntime : собирает /metrics
Grafana --> Prometheus : читает метрики
Grafana --> Jaeger : читает трассировки
CrmRuntime --> Logs : пишет stdout-логи

CrmDll --> Models : читает/пишет ML-модели
CrmRuntime --> Csv : читает файл импорта

Settings ..> PgRuntime : строка подключения
Settings ..> KeycloakRuntime : URL и realm
Settings ..> Collector : OTLP endpoint

note right of AppHost
  Dockerfile публикует Crm.dll в /app.
  Контейнер открывает порты 8080 и 8081.
end note

note right of KeycloakRuntime
  Realm: crm.
  Clients: crm-api и admin-api.
end note

note bottom of ObsHost
  Prometheus собирает метрики с CRM /metrics.
  OTLP Collector принимает трассировки CRM и передает их в Jaeger.
  Grafana используется для просмотра метрик и трассировок.
end note

@enduml
